---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="The world's first superintelligence will be a Minecraft bot">
  <a 
    href={baseUrl}
    style="
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      color: #666;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    "
    onmouseover="this.style.color='#333';"
    onmouseout="this.style.color='#666';"
  >
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor">
      <path d="M8 0a8 8 0 1 0 0 16A8 8 0 0 0 8 0zm3.5 7.5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H5.707l2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708l3-3a.5.5 0 1 1 .708.708L5.707 7.5H11.5z"/>
    </svg>
    Back to home
  </a>
  <div style="margin-top: 1rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.6;">
    <em>
      Coming soon:
      <br />
      1. An AI that is better than us at Minecraft is a superintelligence<br />
      2. An AI that is not better than us at Minecraft is not a superintelligence<br />
      3. Training an AI specifically on Minecraft is the probably the best way to build an AI that is better than us at Minecraft
    </em>
  </div>
